  "description": "Fix Single News Post Display Issues\n\nRestore proper rendering and functionality of individual news post pages that are currently broken.\n\nRequirements:\n- Fix share functionality: Ensure share buttons/links are visible and functional\n- Fix image rendering: Restore proper display of post images (sizing, alignment, aspect ratio)\n- Verify post content layout and formatting render correctly\n- Check responsive behavior across desktop, tablet, and mobile viewports\n- Ensure all post metadata (date, author, category) displays properly\n- Test with posts containing different content types (multiple images, no images, embedded media)\n- Validate that related posts or navigation elements render as expected\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Posts with missing or broken image URLs\n- Posts with very long titles or content\n- Posts with special characters in share URLs\n- Various image sizes and orientations",
